@node "Main" "KeepWB - Contents"

                                  KeepWB
             A handy program to keep the Workbench screen open

You may scoff at such a small program, but it does have it's uses.  I wrote
this  to  keep  the  Workbench  open,  because  the  games I play (and some
applications  too)  close  the  Workbench since they want lots of Chip RAM.
Fair  enough,  but  when the game/application quits, the Workbench tries to
reopen.   Sometimes  this  works,  and  the  Workbench reappears, but other
times, the system goes into a deadlock, causing a crash.  Can be annoying.

So,  I  wrote  KeepWB.   The  idea is simple, perfectly executed, and works
(which helps :).

@{" Licence           " link "Licence" 0} Distribution notes as well
